<div class="container " style="font-family:serif; font-style:italic">
    <div class="events" style="font-family:serif; font-style:italic">
        <p>“What you need, is an Event, to remember for a lifetime.”</p>

        <!--About us-->
        <h2 style="text-align:center"><hr /> About Us<hr /></h2>
        <div class="bg-light">
            <div class="container py-5">
                <div class="row h-100 align-items-center py-5">
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <h2 class="display-4">About us</h2>
                        <p class="font-italic text-muted mb-4 text-uppercase">
                            Planner is a Event Booking and Managment system which creates exclusive events
                            in and outside for Social, Private, Corporations and charity events.
                            Planner contains different venues around Kathmandu city with venue capacity and price.
                            It also have options to select the theme or the design of the event with price included. Catering Services are provided us with food menu and price per plate.
                            Working directly with the events and company saves time and money and guarantees sucess.
                        </p>


                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 d-none d-lg-block"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522389903690-657f5318cf1b?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MXwxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8NTh8fGluZGlhbiUyMHdlZGRpbmd8ZW58MHx8MHw%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=60" alt="" class="img-fluid"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h2 style="text-align: center"><hr /> Our Services <hr /></h2>
        <div class="bg-white py-3">
            <div class="container py-5">
                <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 order-2 order-lg-1">
                        <i class="fab fa-fort-awesome fa-2x"></i>
                        <h2 class="font-weight-light">Venues</h2>
                        <p class="font-italic text-muted mb-4">
                            Buget and luxury venues are accociated with us.
                            All the necsesary information regarding venues are also mentioned. 
                            Customer can Choose the venue according to them.
                        </p>
                        <a class="btn btn-info px-5 rounded-pill shadow-sm" asp-area="" asp-controller="home" asp-action="Venue">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-5 px-5 mx-auto order-1 order-lg-2"><img src="~/asset/designs/heritagegarden.jpg" alt="" class="img-fluid mb-4 mb-lg-0"></div>
