                        </p>
                        <a class="btn btn-info px-5 rounded-pill shadow-sm" asp-area="" asp-controller="home" asp-action="Design">Learn More</a>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 order-2 order-lg-1">
