                        <h2 class="font-weight-light">Catering Services</h2>
                        <p class="font-italic text-muted mb-4">
                            We have created the Menus according to event format. 
                            Vegetarian and non veg menu are also available. 
                            Breakfast and lunch menu are also available with us.
                        </p>
                        <a class="btn btn-info px-5 rounded-pill shadow-sm" asp-area="" asp-controller="home" asp-action="CateringServices">Learn More</a>
